  "content": {
    "problemStatement": "Check if the given year is leap year.\n\n**Note:** A year is a leap year if the following conditions are satisfied:\n\n\nThe year is multiple of 400.\nThe year is a multiple of 4 and not a multiple of 100.\n**Output `YES` if the given year is leap year, else `NO`.**\n\n\nInput Format\n\nThe first and only line of input will contain a single integer YYY - the year.\n\n\nOutput Format\n\nOutput on a single line, `YES` if the given year is leap year, else `NO`.",
    "constraints": [
      "1900≤Y≤21001900 \\leq Y \\leq 21001900≤Y≤2100"
    ],
